channel.title: [562 loading 668] Two questions
channel.description:
Where would I edit my stance and walk animations? I started using DKK's 562 loading 663 client and it makes the animations for walking/standing/running not work anymore, so I was just wandering where I'd edit those..
My second question is, what source goes with DKK's 562 loading 663 client? I've tried 562 loading 668 sources but the crowns and animations are all messed up.. soo would I use one like Eclipse or Dementhium?
Any help is appreciated.

item.title: [562 loading 668] Two questions
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

You’re doing it wrong, your source should match your client.

Example: Using a 474 client with a 474 base.

The only reason people do this is because they can’t program a higher revision.
